            Applied Research Associates, Inc. has an outstanding opportunity for an exceptional scientist or engineer to support a multi-disciplined team that develops methodologies, processes, and technological applications for detecting, locating, identifying, physically and functionally characterizing, modeling and assessing tunnels. The position will require the individual to be expert in applying data science techniques to big data sets such as open source, geographical, and signals intelligence information sets. Advanced experience with trend and pattern analysis is required.  The ability to conduct expert predictive analysis is required. The position develops analysis reports and briefings detailing methods of analysis to support other intelligence analysis.
